    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require schools to offer mental health support to those engaged in bullying",
        "additional_details": "Research shows that bullying can stem from stress and trauma, low self-esteem and difficult home life. I think that if these children were offered mental health support, they would be less likely to bully others. ",
        "background": "I think that schools should be required to offer mental health support to all those who have been found to bully another pupil.",
